Analyzing Activity and Sleep Patterns

Artem Holovko

2025-03-08

  • Installing packages
install.packages("dplyr")
install.packages("tidyverse")
install.packages("readr")
install.packages("ggplot2")
  • Accessing libraries
library(dplyr)
library(tidyverse)
library(readr)
library(ggplot2)
  • Importing .csv files
daily_activity <- read.csv("/cloud/project/dailyActivity_merged.csv")
sleep_day <- read.csv("/cloud/project/sleepDay_merged.csv")
  • Exploring the tables
head(sleep_day)
colnames(sleep_day)
head(daily_activity)
colnames(daily_activity)
n_distinct(daily_activity$Id)
n_distinct(sleep_day$Id)
nrow(daily_activity)
nrow(sleep_day)
  • Creating quick summaries
daily_activity %>% select(TotalSteps, TotalDistance, SedentaryMinutes) %>% summary()
sleep_day %>% select(TotalSleepRecords, TotalMinutesAsleep, TotalTimeInBed) %>% summary()
  • Merge data into combined_data
combined_data <- merge(sleep_day, daily_activity, by = "Id")
n_distinct(combined_data$Id)
View(combined_data)
cor(combined_data$TotalMinutesAsleep, combined_data$TotalSteps)
